{"tid":1284885,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《求音樂奇才》香港的主題曲","createTime":"2019-07-04T10:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T11:01:49.000Z","uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"20a94c21952f0d24bca1704bdaffec58d8328cc4","tid":1284885,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:53:34.000Z","msg":"音樂，除左陶冶性情<br />\n有時亦可以驅走不安嘅情緒<br />\n蘊釀豐富嘅情緒<br />\n堅定人心<br />\n甚至超越對死亡嘅恐懼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無可以代表到香港嘅歌曲或者節奏<br />\n有代表性而且琅琅上口嘅<br />\n（唔好兒夜姨野呢d咁唱完都斷左氣)<br />\n可以助小弟係徬徨無助嘅時候唔會孤單<br />\n諗起一路支持嘅戰友們<br />\n可以拋開恐懼迎難而上邁步向前<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n《Do you Hear The People Sing》<br />\n《義勇軍進行曲》<br />\n《軍艦行進曲》<br />\n呢d咁激昂嘅歌曲<br />\n<br />\n南韓就有過播少女時代嘅歌曲黎迷惑人心<br />\n令人更加胡思亂想<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/amp/realtimenews/20150910002486-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Famp%2Frealtimenews%2F20150910002486-260408&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI7PkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=d7fd4f34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/amp/realtimenews/20150910002486-260408</a><br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n愛國愛黨<br />\n嚴重抑鬱兼自殺傾向<br />\n想有d音樂<br />\n可以令我一聽到就諗起<br />\n我地係香港人唔可以咁易死<br />\n刻入靈魂嘅深處"},{"pid":"f82ec69625a5c5a833ed90ff7377d2574138087b","tid":1284885,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a2cfa37842b5046b32d6d2a4f36b91437cc416f","tid":1284885,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30da63877f6f637e9391f534dbf00989f9665582","tid":1284885,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:55:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"50558fad7aef6a67961f1338fa66712d83006941","tid":1284885,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"49da80b1438b7cb49e124a7c77da4774cc7ffcef","tid":1284885,"uid":265197,"like":0,"d